print ("Welcome to Temperature Alert System")
### User is being asked to input a variable.
temp = int(input("Enter the temperature balue in degrees Celsius: "))
### Conditional statements based off of user input.
if temp < 20:
    print("Too cold. Turn up heating")
elif temp == 20 or temp <= 24:
    print ("Temperature is just right")
elif temp > 24:
    print ("Too warm. Turn down heating.")
